{"tid":1009132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 初一第一跳！牛頭角女子墮樓　送院不治","createTime":"2019-02-05T03:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T12:13:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":151,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"879760c10b490f41d788a2f5aa3746894a017c0d","tid":1009132,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"今早(5日)7時01分，牛頭角樂華南邨奐華樓，一名姓陳(66歲)女子由高處墮下，飛墮地上重傷昏迷，驚動大廈保安員報警。救護車到場將事主送院搶救，惜返魂乏術。警方初步調查相信，事主在上址一梯間墮下，警方於現場無檢獲遺書，正與事主家人聯絡，調查其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190205/bkn-20190205081142349-0205_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190205%2Fbkn-20190205081142349-0205_00822_001.html&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=94ecb06c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190205/bkn-20190205081142349-0205_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2f84f4475e1bc571bc85ec4f015cbbee86f80f15","tid":1009132,"uid":19454,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"首刷"},{"pid":"b8c15e00577ecb769683686da9ee6d479d0294ab","tid":1009132,"uid":229609,"like":300,"dislike":4,"score":296,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"唔可以做豬年第一個出世,咪做豬年第一個刷首抽囉。"},{"pid":"8af32df118e5e2c2c9d928166a4d7c8f581c6d30","tid":1009132,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b8c15e00577ecb769683686da9ee6d479d0294ab","tid":1009132,"uid":229609,"like":300,"dislike":4,"score":296,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"唔可以做豬年第一個出世,咪做豬年第一個刷首抽囉。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2174ea21ba34e05ff39a85cd19d18ffeeee73f83","tid":1009132,"uid":54337,"like":17,"dislike":80,"score":-63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"老貓好折墮。新年新精頭就咪post呢D野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 